--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.0.2 (2019-01-09)
B: Improve return value verification and fix unexpected operator/operand issue
E: Improve Shell script to prevent globbing and word splitting

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-12)
E: Minor Jinja2 filter improvement

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.5.0 (2018-12-10)
F: Add option to set system time offset limit (ntpd_check_time_offset_limit)
E: Remove needless remove tasks

* Version 0.4.1 (2018-12-09)
E: Minor Jinja2 parameter improvement

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-12-08)
F: Redesign 'ntpd_server' parameter
F: Redesign 'ntpd_restrict' parameter
F: Add 'ntpd_check-time' health check

* Version 0.3.4 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove 'ntpd_monitor_mail_subject' parameter

* Version 0.3.3 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove email information from message

* Version 0.3.2 (2018-07-19)
E: Shell script improvements

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-07-12)
E: Minor role improvements

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.1.2 (2018-01-18)
B: Add missing 'ntpdate' dependency

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-01-09)
E: Multiple minor improvements

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-08)
F: Initial release
